metadata.name: artificial imagination
metadata.description:
e9Art - banner art

NFT art sized for twitter banners.
.
.
.
all my life i have been creative, or rather, i have been a suppressed creative. not until the age of 50 did i begin to explore the possibility of being an artist.

and now, at the age of 60, i have come to this place.

it feels as if all my life has been a training ground for this now,

for this world of imagination and play and NFTs and AI text-to-image generators,

and it feels like home ...

digital art by e9Art using disco diffusion and photoshop, May 2022
